      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The emergency power off (EPO) connection is located on the
monitoring controller. The connection is normally closed (NC).</p>
         <note class="- topic/note ">After the EPO is installed the function of the EPO should be
tested. After the EPO is triggered the system needs to be manually
turned on when the signal is no longer active.</note>
